snippet.title: EVNNE (이븐) 'How Can I Do' Official MV
snippet.description:
악동이라는 컨셉으로 K-POP 씬에 등장해 저돌적이고 치기 어린 에너지로 자신들만의 이미지를 구축해 온 EVNNE. 이번 5집에서는 더욱 세련된 비주얼과 완성도 높은 음악으로 새로운 반전을 선사한다. 거칠고 유쾌한 에너지를 내뿜던 그들은 절제된 무드와 섬세한 디테일을 더해, 한층 더 성숙해진 모습으로 또 다른 챕터를 열어간다.

이번 앨범은 사랑이 시작되는 찰나, 상대를 자연스럽게 끌어들이는 EVNNE 특유의 여유롭고 자신감 넘치는 매력을 담아낸다. 멤버들은 각자의 개성과 분위기 속에서 상대를 향한 감정의 신호들을 다채롭게 표현한다.

메인 컨셉 ‘Cheeky’는 자신의 매력을 정확히 알고, 그것을 여유롭게 표현하는 EVNNE의 모습을 그려낸다. 나른하면서도 집요한 시선, 무심한 듯 스치는 표정들은 도심 속 몽롱한 밤거리와 어우러져, 그들만의 유혹적인 분위기를 완성한다. 낯설지 않은 장면 속에서 그들은 이전보다 더 성숙해진 태도로 상대의 시선과 마음을 사로잡는다.
서브 컨셉 'Mellow'는 일상의 거리에서 자연스럽게 마주하는 부드러운 플러팅의 순간을 담았다.
곳곳에 숨겨진 텍스트들과 스치는 시선들은 직접적으로 말하지 않아도 그들이 전하고자 하는 감정을 진솔하고 담백하게 드러낸다. 익숙한 배경과 편안한 분위기 속에서 거리를 함께 걷고 있는 듯한 몰입감과 함께 EVNNE의 또 다른 매력적인 모습을 선사한다.

뮤직비디오는 사랑이 시작되기 전, 마음이 움직이기 시작하는 순간들을 감도 높은 패션 필름 무드로 담아낸다. 자연스럽게 흐르는 카메라의 시선은 직접 EVNNE의 플러팅을 마주하는 듯한 몰입감을 주며, 점차 멤버들에게 이끌리는 감정의 흐름을 따라가게 된다. 여기에 다각도로 전개되는 퍼포먼스와 새로운 연출이 더해져 기존과는 다른 신선한 영상미를 완성한다.

또한, 'How Can I Do' 뮤직비디오에는 EVNNE 각자를 상징하는 오브제들이 등장한다. 앨범의 주제인 플러팅을 오브제들을 통해 은유적으로 드러내며, 감각적인 비주얼로 감정의 결을 시각화한다.

[LOVE ANECDOTE(S)]는 누구나 한 번쯤 겪어봤을 사랑의 시작을 EVNNE만의 방식으로 해석하며, 과감하면서도 편안한 매력으로 또 한 번 그들의 성장과 변화를 보는 이들의 마음에 각인시킬 것이다.

Having been introduced to the K-POP scene as troublemaking rascals, EVNNE has developed their own image filled with passionate and youthful energy over time. Now, through their 5th Mini Album, they attempt to put a spin on their usual appearance through more refined visuals and highly perfected music. EVNNE, by adding a touch of composure and delicate details to their rough, yet vibrant energy, takes another step forward as they open a new chapter in their story.

The album captures EVNNE’s signature easygoing, yet confidence-filled charms that radiate as they naturally draw others in during the first steps of falling in love. In the process, each member expresses their feelings via signals made unique through their personality and atmosphere.

The album’s main concept version ‘Cheeky’ draws upon EVNNE precisely knowing what makes them catch others’ attention and casually showing off these charms. Whether they be relaxed, yet focused stares, or brief flashes of seemingly aloof expressions, the signals combine with dreamy nightscapes to create EVNNE’s particular brand of enticing moods. Finding themselves in familiar settings, EVNNE plays up how their attitudes have matured to grab the attention and hearts of others.
The sub concept version ‘Mellow’ captures a more natural, gentler form of flirting that could be found in everyday settings. Hidden texts and brief glances found throughout the concept subtly reveal a more candid, genuine expression of EVNNE’s emotions. Through familiar settings and comfortable atmospheres, EVNNE draws you into feeling as if they were simply walking down a street with you, showing off yet another charming side to them.

The music video makes use of high-sensitivity fashion film-like moods to represent hearts stirring before falling in love. The natural shift in the camera’s angles gives the feeling of personally being on the receiving end of EVNNE’s flirting, drawing viewers in as if they were gradually falling for the members. The members’ performances shown from multiple angles and novel production techniques also help to create a refreshing visual delight for the viewers.

As well, the ‘How Can I Do’ music video portrays each member of EVNNE with a particular objet to represent themselves. Using the objet to subtly portray the album’s theme of ‘flirting’, emotions are brought to the screen through distinct visual cues.

[LOVE ANECDOTE(S)] takes a look at the beginning of love that anybody would be all too familiar with through EVNNE’s unique views. With the group’s brazen, yet cozy charms, the album will leave a strong impression in the minds of all those who take note of the new level of growth that EVNNE has achieved.

뮤직비디오는 사랑이 시작되기 전, 마음이 움직이기 시작하는 순간들을 감도 높은 패션 필름 무드로 담아낸다. 자연스럽게 흐르는 카메라의 시선은 직접 EVNNE의 플러팅을 마주하는 듯한 몰입감을 주며, 점차 멤버들에게 이끌리는 감정의 흐름을 따라가게 된다. 여기에 다각도로 전개되는 퍼포먼스와 새로운 연출이 더해져 기존과는 다른 신선한 영상미를 완성한다.

또한, 'How Can I Do' 뮤직비디오에는 EVNNE 각자를 상징하는 오브제들이 등장한다. 앨범의 주제인 플러팅을 오브제들을 통해 은유적으로 드러내며, 감각적인 비주얼로 감정의 결을 시각화한다.

[LOVE ANECDOTE(S)]는 누구나 한 번쯤 겪어봤을 사랑의 시작을 EVNNE만의 방식으로 해석하며, 과감하면서도 편안한 매력으로 또 한 번 그들의 성장과 변화를 보는 이들의 마음에 각인시킬 것이다.

Having been introduced to the K-POP scene as troublemaking rascals, EVNNE has developed their own image filled with passionate and youthful energy over time. Now, through their 5th Mini Album, they attempt to put a spin on their usual appearance through more refined visuals and highly perfected music. EVNNE, by adding a touch of composure and delicate details to their rough, yet vibrant energy, takes another step forward as they open a new chapter in their story.

The album captures EVNNE’s signature easygoing, yet confidence-filled charms that radiate as they naturally draw others in during the first steps of falling in love. In the process, each member expresses their feelings via signals made unique through their personality and atmosphere.

The album’s main concept version ‘Cheeky’ draws upon EVNNE precisely knowing what makes them catch others’ attention and casually showing off these charms. Whether they be relaxed, yet focused stares, or brief flashes of seemingly aloof expressions, the signals combine with dreamy nightscapes to create EVNNE’s particular brand of enticing moods. Finding themselves in familiar settings, EVNNE plays up how their attitudes have matured to grab the attention and hearts of others.
The sub concept version ‘Mellow’ captures a more natural, gentler form of flirting that could be found in everyday settings. Hidden texts and brief glances found throughout the concept subtly reveal a more candid, genuine expression of EVNNE’s emotions. Through familiar settings and comfortable atmospheres, EVNNE draws you into feeling as if they were simply walking down a street with you, showing off yet another charming side to them.

The music video makes use of high-sensitivity fashion film-like moods to represent hearts stirring before falling in love. The natural shift in the camera’s angles gives the feeling of personally being on the receiving end of EVNNE’s flirting, drawing viewers in as if they were gradually falling for the members. The members’ performances shown from multiple angles and novel production techniques also help to create a refreshing visual delight for the viewers.

As well, the ‘How Can I Do’ music video portrays each member of EVNNE with a particular objet to represent themselves. Using the objet to subtly portray the album’s theme of ‘flirting’, emotions are brought to the screen through distinct visual cues.

[LOVE ANECDOTE(S)] takes a look at the beginning of love that anybody would be all too familiar with through EVNNE’s unique views. With the group’s brazen, yet cozy charms, the album will leave a strong impression in the minds of all those who take note of the new level of growth that EVNNE has achieved.

「深い霧の中を灯りもつけずに
ふら、ふらり、ひとりさまよい
無邪気な子どもがそう望んだから
気まぐれで手折られた花ひとつ

『ここは遺失物係です』
『何を失くされましたか』
『場所はどこら辺か、心当たりは』

すっからかんの頭とすっからかんのカバンの
底は抜けていた
どこをどう歩いてきたっけ？

何を失くしたのかさえもわからなくて
けれど大事にしてたことは憶えていて
いつか誰かが拾ってくれるでしょうか
探し続けていたら
がらんどうに向き合えたら
いつか生きててよかったと思えるでしょうか

天から賜るこの不幸せに
前触れも、筋合いもない
ふわり舞った蝶がふと疎ましくて
徒に毟られた翅ひとつ

ただ生きていたって意味がさして無いように思えて
諦めることばかり考えます
なんとなくまた目覚めてなんとなく寝落ちている
ひとつも戻らなかったカバンの中
明日も明後日もそうでしょう

大事なものが幾つもあって
ひとつさえ失くしたくなくて
ちゃんと抱えて歩いてきたのに
気づいたら空っぽだ
生きることってなんですか？

何を失くしたのかさえもわからなくて
けれど大事にしてたことは憶えていて
いつか誰かが拾ってくれるでしょうか
探し続けていたら
がらんどうに向き合えたら
いつか生きててよかったと思えるでしょうか
ただ生きていたっていいやと笑えるでしょうか」

誰かを踏み潰す雨が止みますように。
差しのべられた手をちゃんと取れますように。
失くしものをあなたと見つけられますように。
いつか、いつか、いつか、いつか、
いつか。


“Lost and Found”

In a dense fog, without a light on
I wandered and drifted along
Because an innocent child hoped for it
a flower was picked up at a whim

"This is a Lost and Found section"
"What did you lose?"
"Where did you lose it?  Do you have a clue?"

My empty head and my empty bag
were loose-bottomed
Where and how have I walked up to here?

Don't even know what I've lost
but I remember it was precious for me
Will someone pick it up someday?
If I keep on searching
and facing the hollow
will I ever feel happy to be alive someday?

The misfortune graced from the sky
has no presage or reason
A fluttering butterfly was somehow annoying
and its wing was plucked to no purpose

Seems like there isn't much meaning in living a nonchalant life.  
and I just think about giving up
I drift awake again and drift asleep
I didn't get anything back in my bag
likely tomorrow and the day after as well

I have so many precious things
Didn't want to lose any single one of them
So I've been walking holding them tight
but found myself empty 
What does it mean to live?

Don't even know what I've lost
but I remember it was precious for me
Will someone pick it up someday?
If I keep on searching
and facing the hollow
will I ever feel happy to be alive someday?
Will I be able to smile and say it's okay just to be alive?

May the rain treading on someone stop
May I be able to take the hand reaching out to me
May I find with you what I have lost
Someday, someday, someday, someday,
someday

▼みんなへ
ども！ドズルです！

こんなところまでチェックしてくれて、ありがとうございます。
このメッセージを見ているあなたは、ドズル社のことを熱心に調べてくれていますね。
嬉しいです。

動画の中では、伝えられないメッセージをここでは書きます。

まず、いつも動画を見てくれて、ありがとうございます。
動画を見てくれることが一番の応援になります。
もっと応援したい！って人は動画をたくさん見てください！

動画を見てくれる人、高評価やコメントをしてくれる人、ドズル社を話題にしてくれる人、イラストを描いてくれる人、切り抜きをしてくれている人、イベントに来てくれる人、グッズを買ってくれる人、みんなのおかげで楽しく活動できています。
本当みんなありがとう！！！

ただ、応援しすぎて、疲れないようにしてください。
みなさんのペースで、ゆるーくながーく応援してくださいね。
